{"tid":2216579,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"慎入｜留低滿屋垃圾狗屎不辭而別　湖南女租客：願賠償但現在沒錢","createTime":"2020-09-24T20:33:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-25T02:59:04.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"edafac2db77dd692273da59445f87e47240ede3b","tid":2216579,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:33:16.000Z","msg":"近日在湖南長沙，業主劉女士發現租客沒有及時交租，幾番催促之下對方也一直不回訊息，於是找了物業工作人員到出租屋查看。結果發現這名女租客早已不辭而別，她在屋內卻留下滿地垃圾和狗狗糞便，甚至連寵物狗都沒有帶走。<br />\n<br />\n綜合內媒報道，劉女士與女租客的租約在明年6月份到期。劉女士在9月11日在聯繫女租客收租時，對方在翌日凌晨只回覆了一句，之後就沒有回音。過了六七天，劉女士一直無法聯繫這名租客，還擔心她在家中出事。<br />\n<br />\n劉女士此前在物業處留了備用鑰匙，於是聯繫物業工作人員上門查看。工作人員打開門一看，發現屋內有一隻狗以及滿地垃圾，租客卻不知所蹤，於是立即通知劉女士過來。劉女士其後報警處理。<br />\n<br />\n網上流傳的一段影片顯示，民警手拿捕狗網，正嘗試將一隻狗從木梯上抓下來。房間內一片狼藉，到處散落垃圾雜物，除了一些外賣盒等日常垃圾外，還有狗狗的排泄物。<br />\n<br />\n「狗屎、她的衣服被子、泡麵、速食、辣條袋子、飲料瓶子一滿床，天花板上都是蟲子。一桶一桶的垃圾，社區地下停車場包括3樓的大垃圾桶都被我裝滿了。電視機螢幕都爛了，牆也被撓壞了，我把沙發床墊都直接扔了。」據劉女士介紹，事後僅打掃衛生已花費600元（人民幣．下同），預計物品損失4000到5000元。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，劉女士後來已聯繫到這名女租客，對方向她致歉並表示願意賠償，但是說現在沒有錢，希望能給一個期限。目前警方已介入調查。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924837333405697.png/7pGU1ITMU9rT1BTq4Hdq_PdY1Np19sS2sBO2HLATthw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924837333405697.png%2F7pGU1ITMU9rT1BTq4Hdq_PdY1Np19sS2sBO2HLATthw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=0107933d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924938688761857.jpeg/CImLSJVzXvTufcu6tu0ARO1WQnAJL9D84G983OBvfNw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924938688761857.jpeg%2FCImLSJVzXvTufcu6tu0ARO1WQnAJL9D84G983OBvfNw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=276d7240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924941024989185.jpeg/ToieppgwVm-zzX-pEIA-w2O8EwhsifA1QvsbdkL7G3Y?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924941024989185.jpeg%2FToieppgwVm-zzX-pEIA-w2O8EwhsifA1QvsbdkL7G3Y%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e6fc2ee1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924944875360256.jpeg/6NF3mNvWPrgwW2pDvHOHzsGqstZj51LoK12CAytdggM?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924944875360256.jpeg%2F6NF3mNvWPrgwW2pDvHOHzsGqstZj51LoK12CAytdggM%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=a35f53a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924946955735040.png/IzyXvDIL8VFF3MwiGLH3XNEPuu52dSrbi7CmNouwpjY?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924946955735040.png%2FIzyXvDIL8VFF3MwiGLH3XNEPuu52dSrbi7CmNouwpjY%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=22cd6f37&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20200924/385924949036109825.jpeg/rYe2_tAjH6stt8p3R0eyxJnEV2MqR6fxhUv9zIVL_cw?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20200924%2F385924949036109825.jpeg%2FrYe2_tAjH6stt8p3R0eyxJnEV2MqR6fxhUv9zIVL_cw%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=7c897bcb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/-t5TLI4vj_w\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F-t5TLI4vj_w&d=6i5jd82mnfhmr%2B7rEyOheKP8PJJZD286lWcuKEclkJo%3D&h=4fc56503\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/-t5TLI4vj_w</a>"},{"pid":"91b58b6390a2d6241bdc229d9cc9866958a39223","tid":2216579,"uid":12994,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:43:40.000Z","msg":"台灣同大陸d人都係一鳩樣<br />\nd租霸勁污糟核凸<br />\n都唔知點撚樣住得落<br />\n佢地又可以忍受到果下真係神奇"},{"pid":"762d41c087d9ef3256756b6ba9439d9f338cd817","tid":2216579,"uid":32577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-24T20:52:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好恐怖"},{"pid":"82839af7f710c5dd4070cece4c93d